.TH LPF-COMPLETION 8 "June 2026" "lpf 0.3.0" "lpf Manual"
.SH NAME
lpf\-completion \- emit shell completion script
.SH SYNOPSIS
lpf completion [bash]
.SH DESCRIPTION
Emit the bundled bash completion script.
.SH EXAMPLES
lpf completion bash
.SH EXIT STATUS
0 on success.
Non\-zero when validation, planning, or host operations fail.
.SH SEE ALSO
lpf(8)
